name: Rebel Planners
Lore: 'Rebel strategists worked under master tactician General Dodonna. They devised an unorthodox battle plan to destroy the Death Star at the Battle of Yavin.',
Text: 'Use 1 Force to deploy at Massassi War Room or any docking bay. Adds X to total power of your starships at the related system and related sectors, where X = the number of your starships present.',
